    <td>
    <td>{Next}
  <tr algorithm="phony assignment behavior">
    <td class="nowrap">_ = |e|;
    <td>
    <td>{Next}
  <tr algorithm="function call statement behavior">
    <td class="nowrap">|f|(|e1|, ..., |en|);
    <td class="nowrap">|f| has behavior |B|
