      </xmp>
  <tr>
    <td style="width:10%">Parameterization
    <td>`T` is f32 or vecN&lt;f32&gt;
  <tr>
    <td>Description
    <td>Quantizes a 32-bit floating point value `e` as if `e` were converted to
        a [[!IEEE-754|IEEE 754]] binary16 value, and then converted back to a
