        The intermediate binary16 value may be [=flushed to zero=], i.e. the final
        result may be zero if the intermediate binary16 value is denormalized.

        See [[#floating-point-conversion]].

        [=Component-wise=] when `T` is a vector.
  <tr>
    <td>
    <td>

